Step2: Prepare the LeafCutter differential splicing results for visualisation
./prepare_results.R --meta_data_file /Users/hxo752/Desktop/core-projects/22-1MILE-002/group_file.txt \
                    /Users/hxo752/Desktop/core-projects/22-1MILE-002/leafcutter_perind_numers.counts.gz \
                    /Users/hxo752/Desktop/core-projects/22-1MILE-002/siA1vNEG_cluster_significance.txt \
