                    /Users/hxo752/Desktop/core-projects/22-1MILE-002/Rnor \
                    -o /Users/hxo752/Desktop/core-projects/22-1MILE-002/CTRL_A1.RData


Step3: Visualise the results
./run_leafviz.R /Users/hxo752/Desktop/core-projects/22-1MILE-002/CTRL_A1.RData
